This paper involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques for text classification, which are commonly studied in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with the classification of medical data, which could fall under the sub-category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
